OL,3,CTragic baby Victoria had 'no clothes'
OL,4,Con during on-the-run trip, jurors told
OL,6,FA newborn baby was wearing "no
OL,7,Fclothes" during a cross-country taxi
OL,8,Ftrip with her on-the-run parents on a
OL,9,Fcold, wintry night, a court has heard.
OL,11,FWealthy Constance Marten, 36, and her
OL,12,Fpartner Mark Gordon, 49, were
OL,13,Fallegedly motivated by a "selfish"
OL,14,Fdesire to keep their daughter Victoria
OL,15,Fafter four other children were taken
OL,16,Finto care.
