OL,6,FAfter their car burst into flames, the
OL,7,Fdefendants allegedly spent hundreds of
OL,8,Fpounds on taxis and lived off-grid
OL,9,Fbefore their arrests in East Sussex on
OL,10,FFebruary 27 last year.
OL,12,FOn March 1 2023, the baby was found
OL,13,Fdead in a Lidl bag covered in rubbish
OL,14,Finside a disused shed, the Old Bailey
OL,15,Fhas heard.
