OL,3,CTragic baby Victoria had 'no clothes'
OL,4,Con during on-the-run trip, jurors told
OL,6,FOn Monday, jurors heard how a missing
OL,7,Fpersons inquiry was launched last
OL,8,FJanuary 5 after a Peugeot the
OL,9,Fdefendants were allegedly using caught
OL,10,Ffire on a motorway near Bolton,
OL,11,FGreater Manchester.
OL,13,FA placenta and items belonging to
OL,14,FMarten were found in the burnt out
OL,15,Fvehicle on the M61 and a woman was
OL,16,Fseen climbing over the motorway
OL,17,Fbarrier, the court was told.
