OL,4,Con during on-the-run trip, jurors told
OL,6,FA local resident who gave the couple a
OL,7,Flift into Bolton town centre that
OL,8,Fevening described the baby as being
OL,9,Fwrapped in a blanket.
OL,11,FJurors were shown CCTV footage of the
OL,12,Fcouple walking into Bolton bus
OL,13,Finterchange with the baby allegedly
OL,14,Funderneath Marten's coat.
OL,16,FThey took a taxi to Liverpool for
OL,17,Faround #80 before taking another cab
OL,18,Fsome 240 miles, arriving in Harwich in
OL,19,FEssex in the early hours of January 6,
OL,20,Fit is claimed.
