OL,4,Con during on-the-run trip, jurors told
OL,6,FCab driver Ali Yaryar told jurors how
OL,7,Fa man and a woman had flagged him down
OL,8,Fon Edge Lane in Liverpool.
OL,10,FHe said the woman was "shivering" and
OL,11,Fasked for him to turn the heating on
OL,12,Fbefore giving their destination in
OL,13,FEssex.
OL,15,FHe told jurors: "I said this is a long
OL,16,Fjourney. We go to Heathrow airport
OL,17,Ffrom Liverpool for #500 but it's a
OL,18,Fquiet night, I can go there if you
OL,19,Fwant for #400."
