OL,4,Con during on-the-run trip, jurors told
OL,6,FProsecutor Joel Smith said: "What did
OL,7,Fyou notice about the lady?"
OL,9,FMr Yaryar said he saw there was a baby
OL,10,Finside the woman's jacket dressed only
OL,11,Fin a nappy.
OL,13,FHe offered the use of a car seat for
OL,14,Fthe child but she declined, saying the
OL,15,Fbaby was "too small", the witness said.
OL,17,FDuring the journey, the couple
OL,18,Fexplained that their car had broken
OL,19,Fdown and the woman breastfed the baby.
