OL,6,FMr Yaryar said he heard the couple
OL,7,Farguing, with the woman saying "he's
OL,8,Fnot very helpful".
OL,10,FCross-examining for Gordon, John Femi-
OL,11,FOla KC suggested the baby did have
OL,12,Fclothes and only had a nappy on while
OL,13,Fbeing changed.
OL,15,FMr Yaryar replied: "I think the baby
OL,16,Fhad no clothes."
OL,18,FJurors were told it had been a cold
OL,19,Fnight and the man had not been able to
OL,20,Fcalm the baby down as she was crying.
