OL,6,FGiving evidence, Ms Robson said: "She
OL,7,Fasked to extend her stay for another
OL,8,Fnight.
OL,10,F"She only had cash, she had no
OL,11,Fidentification on her or a bank card
OL,12,Fbecause it was left in the car that
OL,13,Fbroke down.
OL,15,F"I told her I would give her about 10
